	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bullingero suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. Cum subito comitia propter inexpectatum cęsaris mandatum solverentur,<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Kaiser <persName ref="1332">Karl</persName> V. hatte am 15. Januar die Beendigung des <placeName ref="1214">Wormser</placeName> Kolloquiums angeordnet; s. ADRG 11/1 208-2 10, <ref target="file#10142">Nr. 112</ref> (vgl. den Abschied vom 18. Januar, ADRG II/1 210f, <ref target="file#10143">Nr. 113</ref>; MO IV 79).</note> scribere ad vos fratres, qualiter voluerunt, non potuerunt.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="146">Philippus</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="146">Philipp Melanchthon</persName>.</note> ipse mihi promisit ad te se scripturum<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>In er Vorlage</hi> scriptum.</note> diligenter esse<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Ein entsprechender Brief ist nicht nachweisbar.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cęterorum unusquisque scribere paratus fuerat.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque oro te, ut, quod non multorum literas adfero ad vos, velitis imputare necessitati.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Argentina tota vos pie colit et diligit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. <persName ref="81">Grynęus</persName> tuus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">2. februarii.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
